Happy mothers day to all the mothers &lt;3 

I know, bit early. I know, you are supposed to love your mother every day. Do you also stay dead till your birthday and die right after?

To those, whose mothers are still alive, or the mother like figure in your life and you have the pleasure of being around her, cherish this moment.  

If you are not around her and not able to see her in person, give her a call.

To those, who have lost your mother, may her soul rest in peace and bless you from heaven. 

To all the beautiful mothers out there, thank you!  You are AWESOME! &lt;3


